sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant DSCICtrl as DSCI Controller
    participant CompNS as Component Namespaces
    participant MonNS as Monitoring Namespace
    participant MeshNS as Service Mesh Namespace

    Note over User,MeshNS: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: Create DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-opendatahub-io-v1<br/>mTLS (K8s API Server)
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Validate CR fields<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-opendatahub-io-v1<br/>mTLS (K8s API Server)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated CR
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created

    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch DataScienceCluster<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: CR created event
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy component manifests<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    DSCCtrl->>CompNS: Create Deployments, Services, etc.<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    CompNS-->>DSCCtrl: Resources created

    Note over User,MeshNS: Flow 2: Platform Initialization (DSCI)

    User->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-opendatahub-io-v1<br/>mTLS (K8s API Server)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created

    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch DSCInitialization<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>DSCICtrl: CR created event
    DSCICtrl->>MonNS: Deploy Prometheus, Alertmanager<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    DSCICtrl->>MeshNS: Configure ServiceMeshMember<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create platform namespaces<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy Trusted CA bundles<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,MeshNS: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant OpMetrics as Operator Metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTP

    Prometheus->>OpMetrics: GET /metrics<br/>Bearer Token
    OpMetrics-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
    Prometheus->>CompNS: Scrape component metrics<br/>Various ports, HTTP/HTTPS
    CompNS-->>Prometheus: Component metrics

    participant UWPrometheus as User-Workload Prometheus
    participant RHOAIPrometheus as RHOAI Prometheus<br/>10443/TCP HTTPS

    UWPrometheus->>RHOAIPrometheus: Federation query<br/>Bearer Token, TLS1.2+
    RHOAIPrometheus-->>UWPrometheus: Aggregated metrics
